column3: str
The time is come! We are presently gathering materials to expand the Moongate Hub!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the Moongate Hub's expansion. We hope you will join our efforts!
The expansion of the Moongate Hub is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
The Moongate Hub now boasts a few helpful upgrades. We thank you all for your cooperation!
Why travel on foot when we can build a Cosmoliner circuit here at the hub? To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the Cosmoliner's construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The construction of the Cosmoliner is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Now that the Cosmoliner is complete, sore feet will soon be a thing of the past. We thank you all for your cooperation!
A proper hub needs a habitation module and a cosmoport for starships. To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the habitation module's construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The construction of the habitation module is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the cosmoport's construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The construction of the cosmoport is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
The habitation module and cosmoport are both ready for occupants. We thank you all for your cooperation!
Reportedly, the mech hangar is due for an upgrade. To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the mech hangar's renovation. We hope you will join our efforts!
The renovation of the mech hangar is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
The mech hangar has now received a much-needed upgrade. We thank you all for your cooperation!
It's time we extended the Cosmoliner into the northwest. To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
The northwestern extension of the Cosmoliner is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Calabash Cove is now just a short hop away! We thank you all for your cooperation!
Next, we'll extend the Cosmoliner into the southeast. To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
The southeastern extension of the Cosmoliner is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
The Cosmoliner now stretches as far as Weddingway's Bower! We thank you all for your cooperation!
For various reasons, we've decided to carve a tunnel into Gleamslope. To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the preliminary stage of tunnel excavation. We hope you will join our efforts!
The preliminary stage of tunnel excavation is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the final stage of tunnel excavation. We hope you will join our efforts!
The final stage of tunnel excavation is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
At last, we can get a good look inside Gleamslope! We thank you all for your cooperation!
Let's extend the Cosmoliner into our brand new Piercingway Tunnel. Presently gathering materials for construction!
The southwestern extension of the Cosmoliner is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
With this Cosmoliner extension, exploring Gleamslope is easier than ever. We thank you all for your cooperation!
The Moongate Hub could stand to be a sight bigger, don't you think? Presently gathering materials for another expansion!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the Moongate Hub's expansion. We hope you will join our efforts!
The expansion of the Moongate Hub is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
The Moongate Hub is officially bigger and better than ever. We thank you all for your cooperation!
What the hub needs now is proper infrastructure: to wit, energization and hydrofication stations. Presently gathering materials for construction!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the energization station's construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The construction of the energization station is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the hydrofication station's construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The construction of the hydrofication station is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
With power and water at our command, the Moongate Hub is now entirely self-sufficient! We thank you all for your cooperation!

column2: Mech Hangar Gamma & Cosmoport Beta Preparations
column3: As of late, the mech hangar and cosmoport are in desperate need of upgrades. To that end, we are presently gathering materials!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the mech hangar's renovation. We hope you will join our efforts!
The renovation of the mech hangar is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the cosmoport's renovation. We hope you will join our efforts!
The renovation of the cosmoport is now underway! Come and lend a paw!

column2: Mech Hangar Gamma & Cosmoport Beta Complete
column3: Both the mech hangar and cosmoport have been outfitted with state-of-the-art upgrades. We thank you all for your cooperation!
Without a lift, we've no means of exploring the lunar nadir─so we'll simply have to build one! Presently gathering materials for construction!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the preliminary stage of nadir lift construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The preliminary construction of the nadir lift is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the final stage of nadir lift construction. We hope you will join our efforts!
The final stage of nadir lift construction is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
At last, we'll discover what lurks within the lunar nadir! We thank you all for your cooperation!
The Cosmoliner could do with one last extension: into the lunar nadir! Presently gathering materials for construction!
The subterranean extension of the Cosmoliner is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
With the Cosmoliner now fully extended, we can travel freely to every last corner of Sinus Ardorum! We thank you all for your cooperation!
Seeing as we now have the population of a small village, it's time our hub looked the part! Presently gathering materials for a truly stellar expansion!
Projects are currently being scheduled for the Moongate Hub's final expansion. We hope you will join our efforts!
The final expansion of the Moongate Hub is now underway! Come and lend a paw!
I present to you our interstellar port town: Lunar Hopopolis, home of the cosmic explorers! We thank you all for your cooperation!
Owing to myriad contributions by artisans like you, we have achieved every last objective outlined for Sinus Ardorum. You've made my dream come true!
